msgstr "本节课，您将学到："

#: chapter10/xinclude.xml:22(para)
msgid "The benefits of partitioning"
msgstr "分区的好处"

#: chapter10/xinclude.xml:26(para)
msgid "How to create partitions"
msgstr "如何创建分区"

#: chapter10/xinclude.xml:30(para)
msgid "How to configure start-up options"
