msgid "When you no longer want to access the new partitions, you can unmount them by right-clicking the <emphasis role=\"strong\">disk</emphasis> icon on the desktop and selecting the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Unmount Volume</emphasis> option from the short-cut menu."
msgstr "当不再想访问此新分区，可以通过在桌面上 <emphasis role=\"strong\">磁盘</emphasis> 图标上点击右键并且从快捷菜单中选择 <emphasis role=\"strong\">卸载</emphasis> 选项卸载它们。"

#: chapter10/xinclude.xml:529(para)
msgid "If you want more control on the mount of partitions,you can click <emphasis role=\"strong\">system</emphasis> menu,and point to <emphasis role=\"strong\">administrate</emphasis>, then click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Disk Utility</emphasis>.The <emphasis role=\"strong\">Palimpsest Disk Utility</emphasis> windows opnens."
