msgid "Type your administrative password. The <emphasis role=\"strong\">Services settings</emphasis> window opens."
msgstr "将打开 <emphasis role=\"strong\">启动应用程序首选项</emphasis> 窗口。"

#: chapter10/xinclude.xml:771(para)
msgid "Select the services you want running by selecting or clearing the respective check boxes."
msgstr "通过选择或清除对应的复选框选择想运行的服务。"

#: chapter10/xinclude.xml:775(title)
msgid "Services Settings Window"
msgstr "启动应用程序首选项窗口"

#: chapter10/xinclude.xml:786(para)
msgid "If you want to add a new item to list,click <emphasis role=\"strong\"> add</emphasis>;if you want delete an item from list,click <emphasis role=\"strong\">delete</emphasis>; if you want to remember the opening software when next login,go to <emphasis role=\"strong\">option</emphasis> tab, and select <emphasis role=\"strong\">remember opening application when logout </emphasis> checkbox."
msgstr "如果想向列表中添加条目，点击 <emphasis role=\"strong\">添加</emphasis>；如果想从列表中删除条目点击 <emphasis role=\"strong\">删除</emphasis>；如果想下次退出时记住现在打开的软件，转到 <emphasis role=\"strong\">选项</emphasis> 标签页，并选中 <emphasis role=\"strong\">注销时自动记住正在运行的程序</emphasis> 复选框。"

# 根据 9.10 进行了更改
#: chapter10/xinclude.xml:798(para)
msgid "If you want greater control over the boot-up services, install Boot-up Manager (bum). You can install bum from the Universe repository. You need to click the <emphasis role=\"strong\">System</emphasis> menu, point to <emphasis role=\"strong\">Administration</emphasis> and click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Boot-up Manager</emphasis>."
