msgstr "在 <emphasis role=\"strong\">系统</emphasis> 菜单上, 指向 <emphasis role=\"strong\">系统管理</emphasis> 然后点击 <emphasis role=\"strong\">分区编辑器</emphasis>。"

#: chapter10/xinclude.xml:971(para)
msgid "In the drive drop-down box, select the hard drive you need to partition by specifying its logical name. The window refreshes and shows you a representation of the drive."
msgstr "在驱动器下拉框中，通过逻辑名选择需要进行分区的硬盘驱动器。窗口刷新并向您显示此驱动器的代表。"

